  <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Free Guide:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/tips\/start-travel-blog\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How&#xA0;to&#xA0;start&#xA0;a&#xA0;Travel&#xA0;Blog<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-create-a-text-shadow-in-instagram-story\">Create a text-shadow in Instagram Story<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By layering text in two colors you give your text more dimension and depth. You basically create the same text twice and place them over each other in a slightly different position.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image nopin\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text.jpg\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks text\"><\/noscript><img width=\"429\" height=\"338\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks text\" class=\"wp-image-9777 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1372px) 100vw, 1372px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text.jpg 1372w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-300x236.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-600x472.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-429x338.jpg 429w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-762x600.jpg 762w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-1029x810.jpg 1029w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-163x128.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-229x180.jpg 229w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-768x605.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-1024x806.jpg 1024w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text-30x24.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150639\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-text.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Step by step:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Create the message you want to put out and copy it<\/li><li>Create another text, paste the text you copied and give it a different color<\/li><li>Place the top text in a slightly different position from the shadow color text<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Instagram Stories tip:<\/strong> You can select any color you like by holding down on a color until a color wheel opens.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-design-with-keyboard-symbols\">Design with keyboard symbols<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know there are symbols hidden inside your keyboard that you can use as design elements? You can scale a simple wave or dot to any size so you don&#x2019;t even note its original form.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image nopin\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-keyboard-modern.jpg\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks keyboard modern\"><\/noscript><img width=\"427\" height=\"338\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks keyboard modern\" class=\"wp-image-9823 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1372px) 100vw, 1372px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150603\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-keyboard-modern.jpg 1372w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150603\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-keyboard-modern-300x237.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150603\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-keyboard-modern-600x475.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150603\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-keyboard-modern-427x338.jpg 427w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150603\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-keyboard-modern-758x600.jpg 758w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150603\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-keyboard-modern-1023x810.jpg 1023w, https:\/\/static.saltinour