ock-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header.jpg\" alt=\"instagram stories music hack\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"324\" alt=\"instagram stories music hack\" class=\"wp-image-9781 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-600x433.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-450x324.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-800x577.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-1080x779.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-163x117.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-250x180.jpg 250w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-768x554.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-1024x738.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-1440x1038.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150636\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-header.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-5-summarize-what-you-are-telling\">5. Summarize what you are telling<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>How many stories do you watch without having your sound turned on? You often find yourself watching stories in public areas and will probably have your volume turned off. Statistics say a huge part of your Instagram Story viewers is watching without sound. <br>A perfect way to directly draw the attention of your Instagram story viewers is by summarizing what you are saying in that same story.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-6-instagram-stories-with-a-reason-to-follow\">6. Instagram Stories with a reason to follow<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It is important to determine why people are following your Instagram account. In the case of our account <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/instagram.com\/saltinourhair\" target=\"_blank\">@SaltinourHair<\/a>; we are a source for travel, photography, and video inspiration.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/