 rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23151250\/tumpak-sewu-best-waterfall-indonesia-java-couple.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>We try to post this as much as possible by applying one of the following Instagram stories tips:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Share useful tips and behind the scenes. <br>What did you just find out about the place you are traveling to? Or what is one of those camera tricks you always do? Share them! <\/li><li>Add location tags to your stories so people know where your stories are taken. <\/li><li>Create an actual storyline. For example; when hiking down a waterfall. Show them the difficulty of the trail, tell them about the duration of the hike, don&#x2019;t be afraid to share real emotions.<\/li><li>Give that story a cliffhanger by waiting a few hours before posting the actual shots of the waterfall. Just make sure it was worth the wait for your followers! <\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Free Guide:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/tips\/start-travel-blog\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How&#xA0;to&#xA0;start&#xA0;a&#xA0;Travel&#xA0;Blog<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-7-add-a-time-or-hyper-lapse\">7. <strong>Add a time- or hyper-lapse<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A hyper- or timelapse is a bunch of photos, pasted together into a video. It will add an interesting new view of a place you currently are. <br>Press record, point it to the sunset or walk from one point straight to another for at least 1-minute and you will have a cool video.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image nopin\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse.jpg\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks hyperlapse\"><\/noscript><img width=\"427\" height=\"338\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks hyperlapse\" class=\"wp-image-9825 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1372px) 100vw, 1372px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse.jpg 1372w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-300x237.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-600x475.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-427x338.jpg 427w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-758x600.jpg 758w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-1023x810.jpg 1023w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-163x129.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150558\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-hyperlapse-227x180.jpg 227w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\