ew 15-second videos. Keep the rule of thumb, don&#x2019;t post more than 4 or 5 stories at once. Post your remaining stories a few hours later. Nobody likes to see a ton of dashes on the top and if they do, they will actually click faster through your stories, which is bad for your conversion.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image nopin\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks.jpg\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks\"><\/noscript><img width=\"448\" height=\"338\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks\" class=\"wp-image-9817 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-300x226.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-600x453.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-448x338.jpg 448w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-796x600.jpg 796w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-1074x810.jpg 1074w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-163x123.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-239x180.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150614\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-768x579.jpg 768w, https:\/\/st