o your most impressive story videos.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/thepreviewapp.com\/how-to-make-beautiful-insta-story-highlight-covers-custom-icons\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Read here<\/a> how to create story covers easily.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image nopin\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-highlights.jpg\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks highlights\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"187\" alt=\"instagram stories tips tricks highlights\" class=\"wp-image-9788 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1667px) 100vw, 1667px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150624\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-highlights.jpg 1667w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150624\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-highlights-300x125.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150624\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-highlights-600x249.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150624\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-highlights-450x187.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150624\/instagram-stories-tips-tricks-highlights-800x332.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150624\/instagram-stor